{"tid":2338644,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"分享吓自己份聽歌「cv」","createTime":"2020-12-24T06:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T11:08:44.000Z","uid":33359,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"9963c2610b82320dcde40ef22c1cd8af7661ea8d","tid":2338644,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"小學時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識聽歌，多數都係跟屋企人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劉德華，陳慧琳，春卷呢批<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中一至中三<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇甲賀忍法貼愛上咗陰陽座<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最鍾意佢首「惡忌判官」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係高登見有人分享creep<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽落幾鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始接觸搖滾樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陰陽座、radiohead<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中四之後時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始瘋狂迷上hard rock<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBon Jovi, guns n rose, aerosmith , led zeppelin, shinedown, system of the down<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩畢業返工時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始聽厭嘈吵既結他同鼓聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追求啲更深層內歛既樂隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPink floyd<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣心情好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有日係youtube聽到首日文歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好熱血好激勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美波「聲嘶力竭」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有日係spotify無啦啦推介kindie<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一聽驚為天人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時都好鍾意聽啲好憂愁既鋼琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGOHO, CIKI, Jiwoo, Ashmute ，坂本龍一，久石讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4111c3911f7516a9a08673e4cc64bd9308bfd29","tid":2338644,"uid":374180,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:48:21.000Z","msg":"又分享 CV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪自爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8079e9cc7fb09103d9d80cc0d305dba873635b2e","tid":2338644,"uid":282792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:48:34.000Z","msg":"聽歌師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cc149b2435fb58a4bd9a59cba4adec056df19b","tid":2338644,"uid":207702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"印：Twice定個Part<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f61346aa495a4311ddd7021efc55d0865b3b26e","tid":2338644,"uid":317378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"以為你係韓流fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c655b9dbbfac36ff1a8e1e56acb0ebfbbeda7a","tid":2338644,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"譯撚左你對話sd 左比你老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\